{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":18,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":null,"text":"这一下虽然凶险，可是终究让咱们认出了对头的面目。","tone":"认真","chapter":25,"line_start":12,"line_end":14},{"speaker":"char_zhang_sanfeng","speaker_name":"张三丰","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"火工头陀内功不行，外功虽然刚猛，可还及不上玄冥神掌，我的伤不碍事。","tone":"平静","chapter":25,"line_start":18,"line_end":20}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[{"id":"skill_xuan_ming_shen_zhang","name":"玄冥神掌","type":"掌法","faction":"faction_yuan_ting","rank":"绝顶","one_line":"阴寒狠毒的掌力，连张三丰亦认为比火工头陀外功更难应付。","techniques":[{"id":"tech_xuan_ming_yin_han_zhang_li","name":"阴寒掌力","type":"掌劲","description":"以阴寒内劲侵入敌体，造成深重寒毒与内伤。"},{"id":"tech_xuan_ming_shuang_lao_he_ji","name":"双老合击","type":"合击","description":"玄冥二老凭默契与深厚掌力联手压制强敌。"}],"progression":["蓄阴寒内力","以掌力透体伤敌","高手合击威力更盛"],"effects":["寒毒侵体","重创内腑"],"combat_style":"阴寒狠辣，重内劲侵蚀","rag_refs":["ch_025:18","ch_025:376"],"source_refs":[{"chapter":25,"line_start":18,"line_end":30,"text":"张三丰称火工头陀外功不及玄冥神掌，并回忆曾与其对掌"}]}],"techniques":[{"id":"tech_xuan_ming_yin_han_zhang_li","name":"玄冥阴寒掌力","type":"掌劲","description":"玄冥神掌的阴寒内劲，可伤人内腑，张三丰称其威力在火工头陀刚猛外功之上。","source_skill":"skill_xuan_ming_shen_zhang","source_refs":[{"chapter":25,"line_start":18,"line_end":18,"text":"火工头陀外功虽然刚猛，可还及不上玄冥神掌"}]}],"factions":[],"locations":[{"id":"loc_wu_dang_shan","name":"武当山","region":"湖北武当","one_line":"本章开端在武当山，张无忌从此安排追踪赵敏及救治武当诸侠。","source_refs":[{"chapter":25,"line_start":1,"line_end":48,"text":"张无忌在武当安排追敌与救治俞岱岩、殷梨亭"}]}],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_zhang_sanfeng","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":25,"line_start":18,"line_end":56,"text":"张三丰说明玄冥神掌厉害并暗喜翠山有后"}]},"relationship_updates":[]}]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":20,"line_end":34,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhang_sanfeng","speaker_name":"张三丰","listener":null,"text":"那一年也是在这三清殿上，我和这人对过一掌，只是当年他假扮蒙古军官，不知到底是二老中的那一老。\n说来惭愧，直到今日，咱们还是摸不清对头的底细。","tone":"认真","chapter":25,"line_start":28,"line_end":30},{"speaker":"char_yang_xiao","speaker_name":"杨逍","listener":null,"text":"那姓赵的少女不知是什么来历，连玄冥二老如此高手，竟也甘心供她驱使。","tone":"认真","chapter":25,"line_start":30,"line_end":32},{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":null,"text":"前赴冰火岛之行，咱们只好暂缓。眼下有两件大事。","tone":"认真","chapter":25,"line_start":34,"line_end":38}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xuan_ming_er_lao","name":"玄冥二老","alias":["鹿杖客鹤笔翁"],"identity":"赵敏麾下高手","faction":"faction_yuan_ting","role":"玄冥神掌高手","archetype":"阴毒强敌","rank":"绝顶","one_line":"玄冥二老以玄冥神掌威震群豪，并在赵敏离开时牵马侍候。","personality":{"traits":["阴沉","狠辣","听命","深藏不露","武功高强"],"speech_style":"本章未直接发言，以行动显威","temperament":"冷峻"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_zhao_min","type":"受命于","intensity":80,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"甘为赵敏驱使"},{"target":"char_zhang_sanfeng","type":"旧敌","intensity":65,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"曾假扮蒙古军官与张三丰对掌"}],"known_skills":["skill_xuan_ming_shen_zhang"],"related_skills":["skill_xuan_ming_shen_zhang"],"rag_refs":["ch_025:28","ch_025:420"],"source_refs":[{"chapter":25,"line_start":28,"line_end":30,"text":"张三丰回忆曾与玄冥二老之一在三清殿对掌"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_zhang_wuji","updates":{"one_line":"第25章中张无忌追踪赵敏、为救俞殷二侠立下三事之约，并在蝴蝶谷确立抗元方略。","source_refs":[{"chapter":25,"line_start":34,"line_end":948,"text":"张无忌先安排追敌救人，后与赵敏击掌为誓并宣示明教抗元策略"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_zhao_min","type":"敌对交易","intensity":82,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"为黑玉断续膏答允三件不违侠义之事"},{"action":"update","target":"char_yang_buhui","type":"青梅旧友","intensity":78,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"听她表明愿嫁殷梨亭，既惊且怜"},{"action":"add","target":"char_chang_yu_chun","type":"兄弟兼部属","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"战场重逢，握手洒泪"},{"action":"add","target":"char_zhu_yuan_zhang","type":"部属","intensity":75,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"接见洪水旗弟子并听其禀报"}]}]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":36,"line_end":52,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_yu_daiyan","speaker_name":"俞岱岩","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"我残废了二十年，便真有仙丹神药，那也治不好的了，倒是救大哥、治六弟他们要紧。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":25,"line_start":38,"line_end":40},{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":null,"text":"事不宜迟，请杨左使、韦蝠王、说不得大师三位，和我一同下山追踪敌人。","tone":"严肃","chapter":25,"line_start":42,"line_end":48},{"speaker":"char_zhang_sanfeng","speaker_name":"张三丰","listener":null,"text":"他能学到我的太极拳、太极剑，只不过是内功底子好、悟性强，虽属难能，还不算是如何可贵。\n嘿，翠山有后，翠山有后！","tone":"欣慰","chapter":25,"line_start":52,"line_end":56}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":4,"line_start":54,"line_end":72,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_yang_xiao","speaker_name":"杨逍","listener":"char_yang_buhui","text":"不悔，你回去罢，好好照看着殷六叔。","tone":"平静","chapter":25,"line_start":62,"line_end":62},{"speaker":"char_yang_buhui","speaker_name":"杨不悔","listener":"char_yang_xiao","text":"是。","tone":"平静","chapter":25,"line_start":62,"line_end":64},{"speaker":"char_yang_buhui","speaker_name":"杨不悔","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"无忌哥哥，我有几句话要跟你说。","tone":"低语","chapter":25,"line_start":64,"line_end":66},{"speaker":"char_yang_xiao","speaker_name":"杨逍等人","listener":null,"text":"他二人是青梅竹马之交，少不得有几句体己的话儿要说。","tone":"调侃","chapter":25,"line_start":66,"line_end":68},{"speaker":"char_yang_buhui","speaker_name":"杨不悔","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"无忌哥哥，你到这里来。","tone":"温柔","chapter":25,"line_start":70,"line_end":70}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_yang_xiao","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":25,"line_start":62,"line_end":688,"text":"杨逍随张无忌追敌，并在战场奉命冲入敌阵"}]},"relationship_updates":[]}]}
