{"segment":7,"line_start":108,"line_end":124,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":"char_yang_buhui","text":"那是六叔神智迷糊中的言语，作不得准。","tone":"认真","chapter":25,"line_start":114,"line_end":114},{"speaker":"char_yang_buhui","speaker_name":"杨不悔","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"不是的！你不明白，我可知道。他后来清醒了，瞧着我的时候，眼光和神气一模一样，仍在求我别离开他，只没说出口来而已。","tone":"认真","chapter":25,"line_start":116,"line_end":118},{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":"char_yang_buhui","text":"我当竭尽全力，设法去夺得黑玉断续膏来，医治三师伯和六叔之伤。","tone":"认真","chapter":25,"line_start":120,"line_end":122},{"speaker":"char_yang_buhui","speaker_name":"杨不悔","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"殷六叔这么瞧着我，我越想越觉爹爹和妈妈对他不起，越想越觉得他可怜。","tone":"悲伤","chapter":25,"line_start":124,"line_end":128}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[{"id":"item_hei_yu_duan_xu_gao","name":"黑玉断续膏","type":"疗伤药物","owner":"char_zhao_min","one_line":"医治大力金刚指断骨伤势的关键灵药。","description":"黑玉断续膏是赵敏掌握的珍贵疗伤药，能接续俞岱岩、殷梨亭被大力金刚指折断的筋骨，成为张无忌被迫立誓交换的核心筹码。","effects":["接续断骨筋脉","救治大力金刚指造成的残伤"],"origin":"西域少林相关疗伤秘药，由赵敏一方掌握","rarity":"稀世","related_characters":["char_zhao_min","char_zhang_wuji","char_yu_daiyan","char_yin_liting"],"related_skills":["skill_da_li_jin_gang_zhi"],"rag_refs":["ch_025:120","ch_025:384"],"source_refs":[{"chapter":25,"line_start":120,"line_end":408,"text":"张无忌誓要夺得黑玉断续膏，赵敏则以此要求他答允三件事"}]}]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_yang_buhui","updates":{"one_line":"第25章中杨不悔向张无忌表明已决定终身相随殷梨亭，展现执拗而深情的一面。","source_refs":[{"chapter":25,"line_start":114,"line_end":170,"text":"杨不悔告诉张无忌自己已决意跟定殷梨亭，并以糖人儿作比"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_yin_liting","type":"恋慕/托付终身","intensity":95,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"明确表示这辈子跟定殷梨亭"},{"action":"update","target":"char_zhang_wuji","type":"青梅旧友","intensity":78,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"坦白心事并回忆幼年相依"}]}]}
{"segment":8,"line_start":126,"line_end":142,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":"char_yang_buhui","text":"你⋯⋯你⋯⋯","tone":"惊讶","chapter":25,"line_start":130,"line_end":130},{"speaker":"char_yang_buhui","speaker_name":"杨不悔","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"我已斩钉截铁的跟他说了，这辈子跟定了他。","tone":"认真","chapter":25,"line_start":130,"line_end":134},{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":"char_yang_buhui","text":"可是你⋯⋯","tone":"惊讶","chapter":25,"line_start":136,"line_end":136},{"speaker":"char_yang_buhui","speaker_name":"杨不悔","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"我不是蓦地动念便答允了他，我一路上已想了很久很久。","tone":"认真","chapter":25,"line_start":136,"line_end":146}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":9,"line_start":144,"line_end":164,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":"char_yang_buhui","text":"我记得。","tone":"悲伤","chapter":25,"line_start":146,"line_end":148},{"speaker":"char_yang_buhui","speaker_name":"杨不悔","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"你给了我那个糖人儿，我舍不得吃，可是拿在手里走路，太阳晒着晒着，糖人儿融啦，我伤心得什么似的，哭个不停。\n那时你很着恼，骂我不听话，是不是？","tone":"温柔","chapter":25,"line_start":150,"line_end":156},{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":"char_yang_buhui","text":"我骂了你么，我可不记得了。不过我心里还是对你好的。","tone":"微笑","chapter":25,"line_start":158,"line_end":160},{"speaker":"char_yang_buhui","speaker_name":"杨不悔","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"我知道。我脾气很执拗，殷六叔是我第一个喜欢的糖人儿，我再也不喜欢第二个了。","tone":"认真","chapter":25,"line_start":162,"line_end":170}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
