{"segment":16,"line_start":264,"line_end":276,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xiao_zhao","speaker_name":"小昭","listener":"char_yan_yuan","text":"什么事？教主睡着啦。","tone":"低语","chapter":25,"line_start":268,"line_end":268},{"speaker":"char_yan_yuan","speaker_name":"颜垣","listener":"char_xiao_zhao","text":"殷六侠痛得已晕去三次，不知教主⋯⋯","tone":"担心","chapter":25,"line_start":268,"line_end":268},{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":"char_yu_daiyan","text":"三师伯，是断骨处痛得厉害么？","tone":"担心","chapter":25,"line_start":274,"line_end":276},{"speaker":"char_yu_daiyan","speaker_name":"俞岱岩","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"断骨处疼痛，那也罢了，只觉得五脏六腑中到处麻痒难当⋯⋯好像，好像有千万条小虫在乱钻乱爬。","tone":"痛苦","chapter":25,"line_start":276,"line_end":278}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_yan_yuan","name":"颜垣","alias":["厚土旗掌旗使"],"identity":"明教厚土旗掌旗使","faction":"faction_ming_jiao","role":"明教五行旗首领之一","archetype":"沉稳传令者","rank":"一流","one_line":"颜垣在武当传报殷梨亭剧痛昏厥，代表厚土旗随张无忌行动。","personality":{"traits":["谨慎","恭敬","沉稳","尽责","寡言"],"speech_style":"轻声禀报，措辞简短","temperament":"稳重内敛"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_zhang_wuji","type":"部属","intensity":70,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"听从教主调遣并及时通报伤情"},{"target":"char_yin_liting","type":"护持对象","intensity":55,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"关注殷六侠痛昏情况"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":["ch_025:268"],"source_refs":[{"chapter":25,"line_start":268,"line_end":268,"text":"厚土旗掌旗使颜垣轻声禀报殷六侠痛得晕去三次"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_yin_liting","updates":{"one_line":"第25章中殷梨亭四肢断折又中七虫七花膏，神智迷乱中牵动杨不悔终身承诺。","source_refs":[{"chapter":25,"line_start":274,"line_end":280,"text":"殷梨亭被救醒后迷糊说看见彩球飞舞，显出七虫七花膏症状"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_yang_buhui","type":"恋慕/依恋","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"清醒时以眼神求她别离开"}]},{"id":"char_yu_daiyan","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":25,"line_start":274,"line_end":278,"text":"俞岱岩说五脏六腑如千万条小虫乱钻乱爬"}]},"relationship_updates":[]},{"id":"char_xiao_zhao","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":25,"line_start":268,"line_end":326,"text":"小昭守门护教主睡眠，后取珠花给张无忌还赵敏"}]},"relationship_updates":[]}]}
{"segment":17,"line_start":278,"line_end":288,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":"char_yin_liting","text":"六叔，你觉得怎样？","tone":"担心","chapter":25,"line_start":278,"line_end":280},{"speaker":"char_yin_liting","speaker_name":"殷梨亭","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"红的、紫的、青的、绿的、黄的、白的、蓝的⋯⋯鲜艳得紧，许许多多小球儿在飞舞，转来转去⋯⋯真好看⋯⋯你瞧，你瞧⋯⋯","tone":"喃喃","chapter":25,"line_start":280,"line_end":280},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"《毒经》","listener":null,"text":"七虫七花膏，以毒虫七种、毒花七种，捣烂煎熬而成，中毒者先感内脏麻痒，如七虫咬啮，然后眼前现斑斓彩色，奇丽变幻，如七花飞散。\n须施毒者自解。","tone":"陈述","chapter":25,"line_start":282,"line_end":286}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[{"id":"skill_du_jing","name":"毒经","type":"医毒典籍","faction":"faction_die_gu","rank":"高深","one_line":"王难姑遗留的毒学典籍，记载七虫七花膏症状与须施毒者自解。","techniques":[{"id":"tech_qi_chong_qi_hua_zheng_bian","name":"七虫七花症辨","type":"辨毒","description":"通过内脏麻痒与七彩幻象辨认七虫七花膏。"},{"id":"tech_shi_du_zhe_zi_jie","name":"施毒者自解","type":"解毒法","description":"指出部分奇毒配方变化繁多，须由施毒者掌握解法。"}],"progression":["熟记毒物症状","辨识毒虫毒花组合","寻找施毒者解法"],"effects":["辨认奇毒","指导解毒方向"],"combat_style":"医毒辨证，不属正面武技","rag_refs":["ch_025:282"],"source_refs":[{"chapter":25,"line_start":282,"line_end":286,"text":"张无忌从王难姑所遗毒经中想起七虫七花膏记载"}]}],"techniques":[{"id":"tech_qi_chong_qi_hua_zheng_bian","name":"七虫七花症辨","type":"辨毒","description":"依据内脏麻痒、眼前七彩幻象等症状，辨认七虫七花膏中毒。","source_skill":"skill_du_jing","source_refs":[{"chapter":25,"line_start":282,"line_end":286,"text":"毒经记载七虫七花膏中毒者先麻痒后见斑斓彩色"}]}],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[{"id":"item_qi_chong_qi_hua_gao","name":"七虫七花膏","type":"毒药","owner":"char_zhao_min","one_line":"以七种毒虫七种毒花制成的奇毒，使俞岱岩、殷梨亭内脏麻痒并眼见幻彩。","description":"七虫七花膏以七种毒虫和七种毒花捣烂煎熬而成，配方变化极多，中毒者先觉五脏麻痒如虫咬，再见七彩幻象，必须施毒者自解。","effects":["内脏麻痒如虫噬","产生斑斓彩色幻觉","需施毒者解毒"],"origin":"王难姑《毒经》记载的奇毒","rarity":"稀世","related_characters":["char_zhao_min","char_yu_daiyan","char_yin_liting","char_zhang_wuji"],"related_skills":["skill_du_jing"],"rag_refs":["ch_025:282","ch_025:380"],"source_refs":[{"chapter":25,"line_start":282,"line_end":286,"text":"张无忌忆起毒经中七虫七花膏的症状和解法"}]}]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":18,"line_start":290,"line_end":304,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_yang_buhui","speaker_name":"杨不悔","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"无忌哥哥，无忌哥哥！","tone":"慌张","chapter":25,"line_start":300,"line_end":300},{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":"char_yang_buhui","text":"是我害了三伯六叔。","tone":"悲痛","chapter":25,"line_start":300,"line_end":302},{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":null,"text":"这七虫七花膏至少也有一百多种配制之法，谁又知道她用的是那七种毒虫、那七种毒花？","tone":"悲痛","chapter":25,"line_start":302,"line_end":306}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":19,"line_start":306,"line_end":328,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_yang_buhui","speaker_name":"杨不悔","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"当真没药可救了么？\n连勉强一试也不成么？","tone":"担心","chapter":25,"line_start":308,"line_end":310},{"speaker":"char_yang_buhui","speaker_name":"杨不悔","listener":null,"text":"嗷！","tone":"悲伤","chapter":25,"line_start":310,"line_end":312},{"speaker":"char_yang_buhui","speaker_name":"杨不悔","listener":null,"text":"他如死了，我也不能活着。","tone":"认真","chapter":25,"line_start":314,"line_end":316},{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":null,"text":"那么我害死的不止是两个人，而是三个。","tone":"悲痛","chapter":25,"line_start":316,"line_end":318},{"speaker":"char_wu_jingcao","speaker_name":"吴劲草","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"教主，那个赵姑娘在观外求见。","tone":"陈述","chapter":25,"line_start":318,"line_end":320},{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":null,"text":"我正要找她！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":25,"line_start":320,"line_end":322},{"speaker":"char_xiao_zhao","speaker_name":"小昭","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"教主，你去还了给赵姑娘。","tone":"温柔","chapter":25,"line_start":324,"line_end":326},{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":"char_xiao_zhao","text":"你倒懂得我的意思。","tone":"温柔","chapter":25,"line_start":326,"line_end":326}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[{"id":"item_zhao_min_zhu_hua","name":"赵敏珠花","type":"饰物","owner":"char_zhao_min","one_line":"赵敏赠出的鬓边珠花，成为她和张无忌之间微妙牵连的信物。","description":"赵敏鬓边取下的珠花原是少女饰物，却在张无忌、小昭与赵敏之间往复传递，既是戏谑信物，也是赵敏要求张无忌收下其物的象征。","effects":["作为私人信物","牵动赵敏与张无忌的情感试探"],"origin":"赵敏随身首饰","rarity":"精致","related_characters":["char_zhao_min","char_zhang_wuji","char_xiao_zhao"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":["ch_025:324","ch_025:412"],"source_refs":[{"chapter":25,"line_start":324,"line_end":414,"text":"小昭让张无忌归还珠花，赵敏又取下珠花要他收下"}]}]},"entity_updates":[]}
