{"segment":22,"line_start":368,"line_end":388,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":"char_zhao_min","text":"区区玄冥神掌，未必便伤得了人。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":25,"line_start":376,"line_end":378},{"speaker":"char_zhao_min","speaker_name":"赵敏","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"那么大力金刚指呢？七虫七花膏呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":25,"line_start":380,"line_end":380},{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":"char_zhao_min","text":"果真就是七虫七花膏。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":25,"line_start":382,"line_end":382},{"speaker":"char_zhao_min","speaker_name":"赵敏","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"张教主，你要黑玉断续膏，我可给你。\n你再对我滥施恶刑，我给你的也只是假药、毒药。","tone":"严肃","chapter":25,"line_start":384,"line_end":390}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_zhao_min","name":"赵敏","alias":["赵姑娘","姓赵少女"],"identity":"蒙古郡主","faction":"faction_yuan_ting","role":"对抗明教与武当的谋主","archetype":"聪慧强势的敌方少女","rank":"二流","one_line":"赵敏以黑玉断续膏为筹码，要张无忌答允三件不违侠义之事。","personality":{"traits":["机敏","骄矜","大胆","善谋","狡黠"],"speech_style":"时而正色威胁，时而俏皮调笑","temperament":"明艳强势"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_zhang_wuji","type":"敌对交易","intensity":80,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"以解药换取三事承诺并击掌为誓"},{"target":"char_xuan_ming_er_lao","type":"驱使","intensity":80,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"玄冥二老听命牵马侍候"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":["skill_xuan_ming_shen_zhang"],"rag_refs":["ch_025:384","ch_025:408"],"source_refs":[{"chapter":25,"line_start":380,"line_end":420,"text":"赵敏承认可给黑玉断续膏，并与张无忌击掌约定三件事"}]}],"skills":[{"id":"skill_da_li_jin_gang_zhi","name":"大力金刚指","type":"指法","faction":"faction_shaolin","rank":"绝顶","one_line":"刚猛指力可捏碎筋骨，是俞岱岩、殷梨亭残伤的直接原因。","techniques":[{"id":"tech_jin_gang_sui_gu_zhi_jin","name":"金刚碎骨","type":"指劲","description":"以刚猛指力捏折骨骼筋脉，造成难以自愈的残伤。"},{"id":"tech_jin_gang_qin_na","name":"金刚擒拿","type":"擒拿","description":"配合指力扣拿关节，使对手四肢受制并遭重创。"}],"progression":["凝聚刚猛指劲","扣拿关节筋骨","以秘药方能续治"],"effects":["折断筋骨","造成长期残废"],"combat_style":"刚猛霸道，专伤筋骨","rag_refs":["ch_025:380"],"source_refs":[{"chapter":25,"line_start":380,"line_end":384,"text":"赵敏以大力金刚指与七虫七花膏逼问张无忌"}]}],"techniques":[{"id":"tech_jin_gang_sui_gu_zhi_jin","name":"金刚碎骨指劲","type":"指劲","description":"大力金刚指造成筋骨断折，必须以黑玉断续膏续治，俞岱岩与殷梨亭皆受其害。","source_skill":"skill_da_li_jin_gang_zhi","source_refs":[{"chapter":25,"line_start":380,"line_end":384,"text":"赵敏以大力金刚指和黑玉断续膏作为谈判筹码"}]}],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":23,"line_start":390,"line_end":408,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":"char_zhao_min","text":"那三件事？\n快说，快说！","tone":"焦急","chapter":25,"line_start":392,"line_end":394},{"speaker":"char_zhao_min","speaker_name":"赵敏","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"又哭又笑，也不怕丑！我早跟你说过，我一时想不起来，什么时候想到了，随时会跟你说，只须你金口一诺，决不违约，那便成了。","tone":"调侃","chapter":25,"line_start":396,"line_end":400},{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":null,"text":"只要不背侠义之道，那么不论多大的难题，我也当竭力以赴。","tone":"认真","chapter":25,"line_start":402,"line_end":404},{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":"char_zhao_min","text":"赵姑娘，若你肯赐灵药，治好了我俞三伯和殷六叔，但教你有所命，张无忌决不敢辞。\n赴汤蹈火，唯君所使。","tone":"严肃","chapter":25,"line_start":404,"line_end":406},{"speaker":"char_zhao_min","speaker_name":"赵敏","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"好，咱们击掌为誓。我给解药于你，治好了你三师伯和六师叔之伤，日后我求你做三件事，只须不违侠义之道，你务当竭力以赴，决不推辞。","tone":"严肃","chapter":25,"line_start":408,"line_end":410}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":24,"line_start":410,"line_end":430,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":"char_zhao_min","text":"谨如尊言。","tone":"严肃","chapter":25,"line_start":410,"line_end":410},{"speaker":"char_zhao_min","speaker_name":"赵敏","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"现下你肯要我的物事罢？","tone":"调侃","chapter":25,"line_start":412,"line_end":412},{"speaker":"char_zhao_min","speaker_name":"赵敏","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"我可不许你再去送给那个俏丫鬟。","tone":"娇声","chapter":25,"line_start":414,"line_end":414},{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":"char_zhao_min","text":"是！","tone":"陈述","chapter":25,"line_start":414,"line_end":416},{"speaker":"char_zhao_min","speaker_name":"赵敏","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"解药立时送到，张教主请了！","tone":"欣喜","chapter":25,"line_start":418,"line_end":420}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
