{"segment":43,"line_start":756,"line_end":772,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhu_yuan_zhang","speaker_name":"朱元璋","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"属下等奉教主传令，赶来蝴蝶谷，本应早到候驾，但途中遇上了一件十分蹊跷之事，属下等跟踪追查，以致误了会期，还请教主恕罪。","tone":"陈述","chapter":25,"line_start":758,"line_end":760},{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":"char_zhu_yuan_zhang","text":"却不知遇上了何事？","tone":"好奇","chapter":25,"line_start":760,"line_end":760},{"speaker":"char_zhu_yuan_zhang","speaker_name":"朱元璋","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"六月上旬，我们便奉到教主令旨，大伙儿好生欢喜，兄弟们商议，该当备什么礼物庆贺教主掌教才是。","tone":"陈述","chapter":25,"line_start":762,"line_end":776}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":44,"line_start":774,"line_end":790,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":"char_zhu_yuan_zhang","text":"都是和尚？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":25,"line_start":776,"line_end":776},{"speaker":"char_zhu_yuan_zhang","speaker_name":"朱元璋","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"不错。那些和尚个个垂头丧气，委靡不振，但其中好些人模样不凡，有的太阳穴高高凸起，有的身裁魁梧。","tone":"认真","chapter":25,"line_start":778,"line_end":788},{"speaker":"char_zhang_wuji","speaker_name":"张无忌","listener":null,"text":"啊","tone":"惊讶","chapter":25,"line_start":788,"line_end":788},{"speaker":"char_zhu_yuan_zhang","speaker_name":"朱元璋","listener":"char_zhang_wuji","text":"吴良兄弟又听得其中一人说：'主人当真神机妙算，令人拜服。\n'另一人说：'这还不算希奇。一箭双雕，却把魔教的众魔头也牵连在内。\n'我们七人假装出恭，在茅厕里悄悄商量，都说此事既牵连本教在内，碰巧落在我们手上，总须查个水落石出， 也好禀报教主知晓。","tone":"认真","chapter":25,"line_start":790,"line_end":796},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"押送者甲","listener":null,"text":"主人当真神机妙算，令人拜服。","tone":"得意","chapter":25,"line_start":790,"line_end":794}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_wu_liang","name":"吴良","alias":[],"identity":"明教洪水旗弟子","faction":"faction_ming_jiao","role":"义军斥候式人物","archetype":"机敏探听者","rank":"三流","one_line":"吴良听到押送僧众者谈及一箭双雕，促成朱元璋等人追查。","personality":{"traits":["机敏","细心","谨慎","重义","行动果断"],"speech_style":"信息由朱元璋转述，内容直接","temperament":"警醒"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_zhu_yuan_zhang","type":"同袍","intensity":75,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"共同追查押送僧众之事"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":["ch_025:790"],"source_refs":[{"chapter":25,"line_start":790,"line_end":796,"text":"吴良听得押送者谈及主人神机妙算和牵连明教"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
